<p style="text-align:center"><img src="images/subgroup.gif" alt="Subgroups" width="475" height="215" /></p>

<p>The Emperor's Hammer Strike Fleet consists of <strong><u>various</u></strong> &quot;Groups&quot; for those Imperial Citizens that wish to join the Empire.&nbsp; Each Subgroup specializes in a different facet of the Star Wars of the Dark Side/Imperial Universe.</p>
<br />
<i>Please note that possession of a particular computer game platform listed below <u>may</u> be required to be accepted into some Groups.</i>

<hr />
<p style="text-align:center">
<a href="http://www.emperorshammer.org/subgroups/the_fringe/fringe.htm" target="_blank">
<img align="middle" border="0" src="images/fringebanner1.jpg" alt="The Fringe" title="Visit the The Fringe" /></a></p>
<p>The Fringe focuses on the Star Wars Massive Multiplayer Online Roleplaying Game (MMORPG)<br />
<a href="http://www.starwarsgalaxies.com" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars Galaxies</strong></a>.  The &quot;adventures&quot; take place online in the always running MMORPG where you create and personalize your own character/avatar in both appearance, style and profession.</p>
<p>
Primary platforms:
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.starwarsgalaxies.com" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars Galaxies</strong></a></li>
</ul>
</p>

<hr />
<p style="text-align:center">
<a href="http://tc.emperorshammer.org" target="_blank"><img src="images/tiecorps.gif" alt="TIE Fighter Corps" title="Visit the TIE Corps" width="400" height="50" align="middle" border="0" /></a></p>
<p>The elite pilots that dominate in competitions and battle with the Rebel forces (i.e. other online clubs).
<u>All</u> pilots must first meet the entrance requirements and will then serve the Imperial Navy as the most elite and highly trained starfighter pilots in the Outer Rim Territories. Entering pilots must first apply and submit a pilot file for review and then be appointed a unit position in the Fleet.</p>
<p>The TIE Corps offers an enormous Mission Compendium holding over 4,000 custom missions for all gaming platforms. Multi-Player competitions (X-Wing vs. TIE Fighter, Balance of Power, X-Wing  Alliance) are held regularly for pilots with the courage to fly in them.</p>
<p>Primary platforms:
<ul>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars:_TIE_Fighter" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars: TIE Fighter</strong></a></li>
