<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X-Wing_vs._TIE_Fighter" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars: X-Wing vs. TIE Fighter and Balance of Power expansion</strong></a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X-Wing_Alliance" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance</strong></a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.freeworlds-tow.net/" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Freeworlds</strong></a></li>
</ul></p>

