<p style="text-align:center">
<a href="http://db.emperorshammer.org" target="_blank">
<img src="images/db-link.gif" alt="Dark Brotherhood" title="Visit the Dark Brotherhood" align="middle" border="0" width="400" height="100" /></a></p>
<p>The Dark Brotherhood is the Group of the Emperor's Hammer that concentrate on the mystical ways of the Dark Side of the Force. Its members are comprised of Force-sensitive beings who are determined and brave enough to answer the call of the Dark Side.</p>
<p>Have you ever dreamt about becoming an intimidating, powerful and feared person? Have you ever felt the hunger for knowledge and power? Are you brave enough for the adventure and facing the uknown? Are you a person who wants to have fun? If you answered “YES“ to any of these questions then you are a person who we are looking for! Join the Dark Brotherhood today and fulfill your dreams!</p>
<p>In the Dark Brotherhood you will gain the unique powers, unattainable to others, and learn the ways of the Dark Side to become a powerful Dark Jedi. Advance in ranks to achieve the right to wield your own lightsaber and gain the knowledge and secrets of your Order. Earn awards and prestige among its members in recognition of your contributions to your bretheren and the Dark Brotherhood.</p>
<p>Game platforms and activities:
<ul>
	<li><a href="http://www.swtor.com" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars: The Old Republic</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="http://www.swtor.com" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars: Jedi Knight (Series)</strong></a></li>
		<ul>
		<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars:_Dark_Forces" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars: Dark Forces</strong></a></li>
		<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars_Jedi_Knight:_Dark_Forces_II" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II</strong></a></li>
		<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars_Jedi_Knight_II:_Jedi_Outcast" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars Jedi Knight II: Jedi Outcast</strong></a></li>
		<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars_Jedi_Knight:_Jedi_Academy" title="Click link for more information" target="_blank"><strong>Star Wars Jedi Knight: Jedi Academy</strong></a></li></ul></ul><br />
Sith pilots of the Dark Brotherhood utilize the same flight sims as the pilots of the TIE Corps.<br />
Creative activities such as fiction writing, graphics creation, Star Wars RPG and many others are also available for participation.</ul></p>

